Terms of Service for VideoAI (AI Video Generator) - Educational Project
Welcome to VideoAI, an AI video generation application developed for academic and demonstration purposes.

IMPORTANT NOTE: This application is created solely for academic projects and testing. It is not a commercial or public product and is not designed for use outside an educational environment.

1. Acceptance of Terms
By using VideoAI, you agree to these terms of service. If you do not agree with any of these terms, please do not use this application.

2. Intended Use
VideoAI is designed to:

Demonstrate the capability of video generation using AI technology.
Serve research and educational purposes.
Provide a testing environment for API integration and feature development.
3. No Personal Data Storage
This application does not collect, permanently store, or process any personal data from users.
Any data you provide (e.g., text descriptions, video generation preferences) is used temporarily during the video creation process and is not retained after the session ends.
4. Generated Content
Videos generated through this application are products of artificial intelligence technology and may be used for academic or personal purposes within the scope of your project.
We are not responsible for the content of the generated videos. You are solely responsible for any content you create using this application.
